com.bmd.jrt.channel

Interface ResultChannel<OUTPUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    OUTPUT - the output data type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Channel, InputChannel<OUTPUT>

    public interface ResultChannel<OUTPUT>
extends InputChannel<OUTPUT>
    Interface defining a result channel, that is the channel used by the routine invocation to publish the results into the output channel.

    Created by davide on 9/15/14.
